    <item>
      <title>美国高昂的糖关税迫使糖果制造商越过边境前往加拿大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/us-sugar-tariffs-make-canada-more-attractive-place-to-manufacture-candy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着各大公司寻求向渴求糖分的北美家庭供应糖分，同时避免美国的保护主义政策，加拿大的糖果产量不断扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/us-sugar-tariffs-make-canada-more-attractive-place-to-manufacture-candy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 13:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称沙特将向外国基金提供阿美约 60% 的股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/saudis-said-to-hand-about-60-of-aramco-offer-to-foreign-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，沙特阿美此次 112 亿美元的股票发售中，外国投资者将获得约 60% 的股份，这标志着该石油巨头的上市方式发生转变，此前该公司在 2019 年上市时，基本上是本地上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/saudis-said-to-hand-about-60-of-aramco-offer-to-foreign-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 13:04:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
